OL,3,CMan jailed after serious collision
OL,4,Cleaves 3 people with life changing
OL,5,Cinjuries
OL,7,FA man has been jailed after a serious
OL,8,Fcollision in Telford left three people
OL,9,Fwith life-changing injuries.
OL,11,FDjay Marques, 26, was driving an Audi
OL,12,FRS6 dangerously along Parkway in
OL,13,FWoodside in November last year, at
OL,14,Faround 5.40pm, when he collided with
OL,15,Fanother vehicle.
OL,17,FHe caused extensive damage to the
OL,18,Fvehicle, which had three people in it.
