OL,7,FAll three people had to be cut free
OL,8,Ffrom the vehicle by the fire service
OL,9,Fand suffered life-threatening injuries.
OL,11,FMarques fled the scene, however due to
OL,12,Fthe impact of the collision his mobile
OL,13,Fphone automatically dialled 999 which
OL,14,Fplaced him at the scene of the
OL,15,Fincident.
OL,17,FOfficers searched for Marques, who
OL,18,Feventually handed himself into police
OL,19,Fin June this year.
