OL,7,FHe was subsequently charged with three
OL,8,Fcounts of causing serious injury by
OL,9,Fdangerous driving and pleaded guilty
OL,10,Fto the charges in October at
OL,11,FShrewsbury Crown Court.
OL,13,FOfficers carried out a manhunt for
OL,14,FMarques, who eventually handed himself
OL,15,Fin to police in June this year. He was
OL,16,Fsubsequently charged with three counts
OL,17,Fof causing serious injury by dangerous
OL,18,Fdriving and pleaded guilty to the
OL,19,Fcharges in October at Shrewsbury Crown
OL,20,FCourt.
