OL,7,FOn Friday, November 29th, Marques was
OL,8,Fgiven a three and a half year
OL,9,Fcustodial sentence, as well as a three
OL,10,Fand half year driving ban at
OL,11,FShrewsbury Crown Court for the
OL,12,Fcollision.
OL,14,FWest Mercia Police, PC Ben Ward, from
OL,15,Fthe force's Serious Collision
OL,16,FInvestigation Unit, said: "Marques
OL,17,Factions that night not only left three
OL,18,Fpeople with life-changing injuries but
OL,19,Falso delayed us getting any form of
OL,20,Fjustice for them after he fled the
OL,21,Fscene.
